{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":537,"text":"My work focuses on the connection of"},{"time":3054,"text":"both thinking about our community life"},{"time":6561,"text":"being part of the environment"},{"time":8221,"text":"where architecture grows from the natural"},{"time":10509,"text":"local conditions and traditions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13981,"text":"Today I brought two recent projects"},{"time":16130,"text":"as an example of this."},{"time":18403,"text":"Both projects are in emerging countries,"},{"time":20479,"text":"one in Ethiopia and another one in Tunisia."},{"time":23518,"text":"And also they have in common"},{"time":25277,"text":"that the different analyses from different perspectives"},{"time":28309,"text":"becomes an essential part of the final piece of architecture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32892,"text":"The first example started with an invitation"},{"time":35634,"text":"to design a multistory shopping mall"},{"time":37657,"text":"in Ethiopia's capital city Addis Ababa."},{"time":39962,"text":"And this is the type of building"},{"time":42257,"text":"we were shown as an example, to my team and myself,"},{"time":45082,"text":"of what we had to design."},{"time":47246,"text":"At first, the first thing I thought was,"},{"time":49321,"text":"I want to run away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51271,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":53332,"text":"After seeing a few of these buildings --"},{"time":55640,"text":"there are many in the city --"},{"time":57440,"text":"we realized that they have three very big points."},{"time":60882,"text":"First, these buildings, they are almost empty"},{"time":62978,"text":"because they have very large shops"},{"time":64759,"text":"where people cannot afford to buy things."},{"time":67730,"text":"Second, they need tons of energy to perform"},{"time":70570,"text":"because of the skin treatment with glass"},{"time":72738,"text":"that creates heat in the inside,"},{"time":74706,"text":"and then you need a lot of cooling."},{"time":76346,"text":"In a city where this shouldn't happen"},{"time":78307,"text":"because they have really mild weather"},{"time":80202,"text":"that ranges from 20 to 25 degrees the whole year."},{"time":83951,"text":"And third is that their image has nothing to do"},{"time":87141,"text":"with Africa and with Ethiopia."},{"time":89296,"text":"It is a pity in a place that has such rich culture and traditions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94898,"text":"Also during our first visit to Ethiopia,"},{"time":97718,"text":"I was really captivated by the old merkato"},{"time":99846,"text":"that is this open-air structure"},{"time":102027,"text":"where thousands of people, they go and buy things"},{"time":103919,"text":"every day from small vendors."},{"time":106286,"text":"And also it has this idea of the public space"},{"time":108574,"text":"that uses the outdoors to create activity."},{"time":111816,"text":"So I thought, this is what I really want to design,"},{"time":115182,"text":"not a shopping mall."},{"time":116971,"text":"But the question was how we could do a multistory,"},{"time":120251,"text":"contemporary building with these principles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123140,"text":"The next challenge was when we looked at the site,"},{"time":125596,"text":"that is, in a really growing area of the city,"},{"time":128144,"text":"where most of these buildings that you see in the image,"},{"time":130628,"text":"they were not there."},{"time":132230,"text":"And it's also between two parallel streets"},{"time":134902,"text":"that don't have any connection for hundreds of meters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137269,"text":"So the first thing we did was to create a connection"},{"time":140663,"text":"between these two streets,"},{"time":142399,"text":"putting all the entrances of the building."},{"time":144598,"text":"And this extends with an inclined atrium"},{"time":147383,"text":"that creates an open-air space in the building"},{"time":149711,"text":"that self-protects itself with its own shape"},{"time":152440,"text":"from the sun and the rain."},{"time":154242,"text":"And around this void"},{"time":155898,"text":"we placed this idea of the market with small shops,"},{"time":159201,"text":"that change in each floor because of the shape of the void."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162971,"text":"I also thought, how to close the building?"},{"time":165242,"text":"And I really wanted to find a solution"},{"time":167152,"text":"that would respond to the local climate conditions."},{"time":170615,"text":"And I started thinking about the textile"},{"time":172723,"text":"like a shell made of concrete"},{"time":174604,"text":"with perforations that would let the air in,"},{"time":178175,"text":"and also the light, but in a filtered way."},{"time":180799,"text":"And then the inspiration came from these beautiful \npatterns of the Ethiopian women's dresses."},{"time":186603,"text":"That they have fractal geometry properties"},{"time":188778,"text":"and this helped me to shape the whole facade."},{"time":190909,"text":"And we are building that"},{"time":192514,"text":"with these small prefabricated pieces"},{"time":194655,"text":"that are the windows that let the air and the light"},{"time":198093,"text":"in a controlled way inside the building."},{"time":200075,"text":"And this is complemented by these small colored glasses"},{"time":202457,"text":"that use the light from the inside of the building"},{"time":205060,"text":"to light up the building at night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207946,"text":"With these ideas it was not easy first to convince the developers"},{"time":212068,"text":"because they were like,"},{"time":213224,"text":"\"This is not a shopping mall. We didn't ask for that.\""},{"time":215912,"text":"But then we all realized that this idea of the market"},{"time":221721,"text":"happened to be a lot more profitable than the idea of the shopping mall"},{"time":224495,"text":"because basically they had more shops to sell."},{"time":227215,"text":"And also that the idea of the facade was much, much cheaper,"},{"time":231289,"text":"not only because of the material compared with the glass,"},{"time":233517,"text":"but also because we didn't need to have air conditioning anymore."},{"time":236205,"text":"So we created some budget savings"},{"time":238362,"text":"that we used to implement the project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240259,"text":"And the first implementation was to think"},{"time":242191,"text":"about how we could make the building self-sufficient in terms of energy"},{"time":245431,"text":"in a city that has electricity cuts almost every day."},{"time":248765,"text":"So we created a huge asset by placing photovoltaics there on the roof."},{"time":252982,"text":"And then under those panels"},{"time":255063,"text":"we thought about the roof like a new public space with gathering areas and bars"},{"time":258799,"text":"that would create this urban oasis."},{"time":261613,"text":"And these porches on the roof,"},{"time":263403,"text":"all together they collect the water to reuse for sanitation on the inside."},{"time":268139,"text":"Hopefully by the beginning of next year, because we are already on the fifth floor of the construction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273301,"text":"The second example is a master plan"},{"time":276356,"text":"of 2,000 apartments and facilities in the city of Tunis."},{"time":279635,"text":"And for doing such a big project, the biggest project I've ever designed,"},{"time":283569,"text":"I really needed to understand the city of Tunis,"},{"time":285834,"text":"but also its surroundings and the tradition and culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289956,"text":"During that analysis I paid special attention to the medina"},{"time":293064,"text":"that is this 1,000-year-old structure that used to be closed by a wall,"},{"time":297041,"text":"opened by twelve different gates, connected by almost straight lines."},{"time":301490,"text":"When I went to the site, the first design operation we did"},{"time":305859,"text":"was to extend the existing streets, creating 12 initial blocks"},{"time":309879,"text":"similar in size and characteristics to the ones we have in Barcelona"},{"time":313063,"text":"and other cities in Europe with these courtyards."},{"time":316054,"text":"On top of that, we selected some strategic points"},{"time":318839,"text":"reminded of this idea of the gates and connecting them by straight lines,"},{"time":322040,"text":"and this modified this initial pattern."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324810,"text":"And the last operation was to think about the cell,"},{"time":327260,"text":"the small cell of the project, like the apartment,"},{"time":329950,"text":"as an essential part of the master plan."},{"time":331728,"text":"And for that I thought, what would be the best orientation"},{"time":334901,"text":"in the Mediterranean climate for an apartment?"},{"time":337200,"text":"And it's north-south, because it creates a thermal difference between both sides of the house"},{"time":341963,"text":"and then a natural ventilation."},{"time":344826,"text":"So we overlap a pattern that makes sure that most of the apartments"},{"time":348412,"text":"are perfectly oriented in that direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350552,"text":"And this is the result"},{"time":352012,"text":"that is almost like a combination of the European block and the Arab city."},{"time":355777,"text":"It has these blocks with courtyards,"},{"time":357375,"text":"and then on the ground floor"},{"time":358498,"text":"you have all these connections for the pedestrians."},{"time":360634,"text":"And also it responds to the local regulations that establish"},{"time":363741,"text":"a higher density on the upper levels and a lower density on the ground floor."},{"time":367404,"text":"And it also reinforces this idea of the gates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370950,"text":"The volume has this connecting shape"},{"time":372842,"text":"that shades itself with three different types of apartments"},{"time":376144,"text":"and also lets the light go on the ground floor in a very dense neighborhood"},{"time":379787,"text":"And in the courtyards there are the different facilities,"},{"time":382687,"text":"such as a gym and a kindergarten"},{"time":384417,"text":"and close by, a series of commercial [spaces] that bring activity to the ground floor."},{"time":388487,"text":"The roof, which is my favorite space of the project"},{"time":391287,"text":"is almost like giving back to the community the space taken by the construction."},{"time":394997,"text":"And it's where all the neighbors, they can go up and socialize,"},{"time":397281,"text":"and do activities such as having a two-kilometer run in the morning,"},{"time":400818,"text":"jumping from one building to another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404202,"text":"These two examples,"},{"time":406561,"text":"they have a common approach in the design process."},{"time":409945,"text":"And also, they are in emerging countries where you can see"},{"time":412524,"text":"the cities literally growing."},{"time":414670,"text":"In these cities, the impact of architecture in people's lives of today and tomorrow"},{"time":419411,"text":"changes the local communities and economies at the same speed as the buildings grow."},{"time":424552,"text":"For this reason, I see even more importance"},{"time":427160,"text":"to look at architecture finding simple but affordable solutions"},{"time":432190,"text":"that enhance the relationship between the community and the environment"},{"time":436251,"text":"and that aim to connect nature and people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440169,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442067,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}